Filed In The U.S. Circuit Court of Washington
United States Circuit Court For the District of Washington
In the matter of the Petition of Char. W. Nordstrom for petition w Habeas Corpus and relief thereon
against Ed. W. Cudahee Sheriff of King County Wash
To the Clerk of the above entitled court:

You will please enter my appearance as Counsel for Petitioner Char. W. Nordstrom in above entitled cause wherein the petitioner seeks writ of Habeas Corpus and relief thereon imprisonment as prayed thereon
Notice-Attorneys will please endorese their own Filings. Rule 47.
